[It is gratifying to see that the Malaysians are getting to the heart of
the epidemiologic matter. It will not be easier to end this nightmare.
No one knows that simple hand-washing will prevent infection but it
certainly cannot hurt to maintain a cleanliness barrier and to avoid or
eliminate fomites. - Mod.CHC
